# Run this script to compile jcblock. First make it executable
# with: chmod +x makejcblock
# Then run it with: ./makejcblock

# For first-time users, use this compile command:
gcc -o jcblock jcblock.c truncate.c -lm

# If you want to try additional options, activate them in
# jcblock.c (i.e., uncomment DO_TONES, SEND_ON_NETWORK etc.) and
# use this compile command:
#gcc -o jcblock jcblock.c tones.c truncate.c radio.c -lasound -ldl -lm
